# Auto detect text files and normalize line endings to LF
* text=auto

# Text files
*.md text eol=lf
*.js text eol=lf
*.py text eol=lf
*.java text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
*.bash text eol=lf

# Windows batch files
*.bat text eol=crlf
*.cmd text eol=crlf

# Binary files
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.mov binary
*.mp4 binary
*.zip binary
*.gz binary
*.tar binary
*.pdf binary
*.xlsx binary
*.xls binary
```

**For Mac-only projects**, you could use a minimal version:
```
* text=auto
*.md text
*.js text
*.py text
